<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> der
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> armlewte von Hagenhawsen czu
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden kumen von eins holcz wegen,
                        doselbst bey Hagenhawsen gelegen; <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> armlewte darynne durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> dinste <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        gnediklich <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen wöllet, also warczu
                        sie reht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz sie dabey
                            <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> gnaden des wol
                                <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<add>in</add> festo pasce die <expan>s<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>da</expan> anno
                            xo<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
